- case classes are standard classes with a special modifier: case

- case modifier signals the compiler to assume certain things about 
  the class and to define certain boilrt-plate based on those assumptions.

- Constructor parameters become public 'fields'

- Methods toString(), equals() and hashCode() are defined
  based on the constructor fields

- A companion object containing:
  An apply() constructor based on the class constructor 
  An extractor based on constuctor fields
